quran[89]{c,v,t}:
  43,1,"Ha, Mim."
  43,2,"Nditsuba khu Eshitabu shinoosinjia."
  43,3,"Toto efwe khwachikhola Ikurani yolwarabu khomunyoole okhumanya."
  43,4,"Ne toto eyo ili nende amaandiko karula khwifwe, niyoluyali, eyamachesi."
  43,5,"Koo, khuleshe okhubetsulisia mana khwibilile mbu shichila muli Abandu babura eshichelo?"
  43,6,"Ne ni Abarumwa benga bakhwaranjilila okhuruma khubandu bakhale?"
  43,7,"Ne abulaho Omurumwa yesiyesi wabetselanga halali bamukholelanga omubayo."
  43,8,"Ne khwasishia balia abali nende amaani okhushila bo. Ne okhuchelaasia khwa Abandu ba khale khwamala okhubura."
  43,9,"Ne nobareba mbu: “Ni wina waloonga likulu nende eshialo?” Toto balaboola mbu: “Nyasaye Owamaani, Omumanyi muno niye wabiloonga.”"
  43,10,"Ulia wabakwalasilia liloba shinga obulili, mana nabarereramwo tsinjila khomunyoole okhulunjikha."
  43,11,"Ne ni ulia wishinjia amaatsi okhurula mwikulu khushichelo, nikhukalamusilia liloba liafwa, ne endio nilwa mulirusibwamwo."
  43,12,"Ne niye owaloonga buli eshindu eshisatsa nende eshikhasi, mana nabakasilia ebininwamwo biomumaatsi nende tsisolo tsiamuninangakhwo."
  43,13,"Kho mwikhale obulayi khumikongo chiatsio, mana mwitsulile emikabo chia Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi nimwakhamala okhwikhalakhwo obulayi, mana muboole mbu: “Obutswenufu nibwa ulia owakhuanguyilia bino mbu khubikhonyele, ne shikhwakhakholele abeene kano tawe."
  43,14,"Ne toto khulikalukha ewa Nyasaye wefu Omulesi.”"
  43,15,"Ne mubasumba bebe bamukholelanga omukabo. Toto Omundu nomukhayi owahabulafu muno khumikabo chia Nyasaye."
  43,16,"Nohomba yebukulila Abana abakhaana mubiloonje bibie biayaloonga, mana nabawulila enywe Abana abasiani?"
  43,17,"Ne yesiyesi mubo naboolelwa khukabachelasinjiakhwo Nyasaye Owetsimbabaasi, obweni bubwe bumaliyanga ti, ne yetsulamwo oburuma."
  43,18,"Koo, ulia wakhusibwa muburone, ne shanyala okhwinoosia obulai nayingananga tawe?"
  43,19,"Ne bakhola Abamalaika abali abasumba ba Omunji Wetsimbabaasi mbu naabakhasi! Koo, balolakhwo okhulongwa khwabu? Obuloli bwabu bulihandikwa ne balireebwa."
  43,20,"Ne baboolanga mbu: “Omunji Wetsimbabaasi yenyanga, efwe shikhwakhabalaamile tawe.” Shibamanyile ako tawe. Babula liababoola halali obubeyi butswa."
  43,21,"Koo, khwabahelesiakhwo eshitabu imbeli wa shino, mana batilananga ninashio nibashiloonda?"
  43,22,"Halali baboola mbu: “Toto efwe khwanyoola bapapa befu nibaloondanga idini yabu yilobole, ne efwe khuloondanga mubilenje biabu.”"
  43,23,"Ne endio shikhwarumakhwo imbeli wuwo omwikanyilisi mulukongo lwosilwosi tawe, halali balia bali mubwokholo baboola mbu: “Efwe khwanyoola bapapa befu nibaloondanga idini yabu ilobole, nafu khuloondanga mubilenje biabu.”"
  43,24,"Naboola mbu: “Kata nebarerera kobulunjifu obulayi okhushila biamwanyoola basenywe nibali ninabwo?” Nibaboola mbu: “Efwe toto khukhayile sa akamwarumwa ninako ako.”"
  43,25,"Mana nikhubatila khumabii kabakhola. Kho hengakhwo, indukho yabakhayi shingala yali."
  43,26,"Ne olwa Ibrahim yaboolela Samwana nende Abandu bebe mbu: “Toto esie endi ehale muno nende kamulaamanga ako."
  43,27,"Halali ulia owalonga esie niye ulalunjisia.”"
  43,28,"Ne nalikhola lino okhuba likhuwa liatong’a khulwibulo lulwe khobanyoole okhukalukha."
  43,29,"Halali khwasangasia bano nende abebusi babu okhula shinga obwatoto bwaboolela nende Omurumwa wa habulafu."
  43,30,"Ne olwa obwatoto bwaboolela, baboola mbu: “Buno ni obulosi, ne efwe toto khubukhayile.”"
  43,31,"Ne nibaboola mbu: “Shichila shina Ikurani ino nileshibwa khumusatsa omukhongo mumatokho amakhongo kabili kano?”"
  43,32,"Koo, abo nibo bakabanga tsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi? Efwe khwabakabila obulamu bwabu bwokhushialo hakari wabu, ne nikhuninia abaandi mubo okhushila abaandi khubichelo kho abaandi mubo banyoole okhukholela abaandi emilimo. Ne tsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi tsishila bioosi biabakhung’asinjia."
  43,33,"Ne bikhayanga okhuba mbu abandu banyala okhuba omukanda mulala, khwakhakholele balia abakhaya Nyasaye wabu Omulesi tsinzu tsiabu okhuba nende ebitsafu bia ifedha nende tsingasi tsiabu tsioosi tsiabaninilanga."
  43,34,"Nende emiliango chietsinzu tsiabu nende ebitanda biabayiekhangakhwo."
  43,35,"Nende oburone. Halali ako shini shiosishiosi tawe, halali ni omwikhoyo kwobulamu bwomushialo butswa. Ne mwikulu ili ewa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niya balia abaria Nyasaye."
  43,36,"Ne ulia wikhola omuwofu khumakhuwa ka Nyasaye, khulamukholela Shetani abe omwitsa ulalekhana ninaye tawe."
  43,37,"Ne toto bo babekalilanga injila muno, ne abeene baparanga mbu balunjika."
  43,38,"Okhula shinga balikhwitsila, baliboola mbu: “Oh, manyanga bibetsanga ehale hakari wanje ninawe shinga ebukwe nende mumbo. Oli omwitsa omubii muno.”"
  43,39,"Ne khulwo khuba mbu mwakhola obubii, shibulaho shilabakhoonya enywe olwa lelo mbu musanganga mwesi mushinyasio."
  43,40,"Koo, onyala okhukhola abekala amarwi bawulile, nohomba onyala okhulunjisia abawofu bali mubukori bwa habulafu?"
  43,41,"Ne kata nikhukhuhiniaho, toto efwe khwitsa okhubarunga imongo."
  43,42,"Nohomba khulakhwechesia akakhwabalaka, nafu toto khuli nende obunyali khubo."
  43,43,"Mana tilana nende akawafimbulilwa, toto ewe oli khunjila ingololofu."
  43,44,"Ne toto kano ni ametsulisio khwiwe nende khubandu bao, ne mulitsa okhurebwa."
  43,45,"Ne reba Abakhwaruma imbeli wuwo mubarumwa befu, koo, khwakhola abanyasaye bandi balamwe balali Nyasaye Owetsimbabaasi tawe?"
  43,46,"Ne toto khwaruma Musa nende ebimanyisio biefu khu Firauni nende abakhongo baye, mana naboola mbu: “Esie toto endi Omurumwa wa Nyasaye Omulesi webilonje bioosi.”"
  43,47,"Olwa yabetsela nende ebimanyisio biefu, lola, nibachaka okhubitseshela khumubayo."
  43,48,"Ne shikhwabechesia eshimanyisio shiosishiosi tawe, halali neshikhongo muno okhushila eshindi shilia, mana nikhubatila khushinyasio khobanyoole okhukalukha."
  43,49,"Nibaboola mbu: “Ewe omulosi, khusabile Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi indache yayakhulaka, (nakhurusiliaho eshinyasio shino luno), efwe toto khulalunjikha.”"
  43,50,"Olwa khwabarusiliaho eshinyasio esho, lola habwene nahabwene nibafunaka indache."
  43,51,"Firauni nalaanga mubandu bebe nababoolela mbu: “Enywe Abandu banje, shendi Omwami welitokho lia Misri, ne emialo chino chiburanga hasi wanje. Koo, shimulolangakhwo tawe?"
  43,52,"Nohomba esie shendi noluyali okhushila omuteshele uno, ulanyala okhwinoosia amakhuwa obulayi tawe?"
  43,53,"Ne shichila shina nalafwalwa ebifwalo bia mumakhono, bieyidhahabu, nohomba yetse nende Abamalaika halala ninaye (bokhumukhoonya)?”"
  43,54,"Mana nabayila Abandu bebe mana nibamufuchilila, toto abo bali Abandu abakori."
  43,55,"Kho olwa bakhusinyisia, khwabatila obutinyu mana nikhubasishia mumaatsi boosi."
  43,56,"Ne nikhubakhola okhuba abaranjilili nende eshilolelo khubandu beyinyuma."
  43,57,"Ne olwa Omwana wa Mariam yachelasibwa (nende Adam), lola, Abandu bo boopa oluyoka khulwa elo."
  43,58,"Mana nibaboola mbu: “Abanyasaye befu nibo abalayi nohomba Ye?” Ne shibakhuchelasilia bario tawe halali amayinji butswa. Ne abo ni Abandu bokhusolana butswa."
  43,59,"Naye (Isa) shali nobunyali tawe halali yali Omusumba wakhwahelesia tsimbabaasi mana nikhumukhola eshilolelo khubana ba Israili."
  43,60,"Ne khwenyanga, khwakharerere Abamalaika khushialo nibaloondana."
  43,61,"Ne toto ye (Isa) ni eshimanyisio shieyinyanga yeyindukho. Kho mulakhatema mwakanakana khwelio tawe, ne munondekhwo. Ino niyo injila ingololofu."
  43,62,"Ne toto Shetani alakhatema yabekalila tawe. Toto ye ni Omusuku wenyu owa habulafu."
  43,63,"Ne olwa Isa yetsa nende ebifune bia habulafu, yaboola mbu: “Toto ebeetsele nende amachesi nende okhubenoosilia kalia akamukabukhanangamwo, kho rie Nyasaye mana muuwulile esie."
  43,64,"Toto Nyasaye niye Omulesi wanje nende Omulesi wenyu, kho mumulaame yenyene butswa. Ino niyo injila ingololofu.”"
  43,65,"Mana emikanda nichikabukhana abeene khubeene. Kho eshinyasio shieyinyanga indulu shiliba khu balia bakhola amabii."
  43,66,"Koo, shina shiabaliindanga, halali indukho ibetsele mapwoka nabo nibalamanyile tawe."
  43,67,"Abeetsa ba mbusia ngonia inyanga eyo baliba Abasuku abeene khubeene, halali balia abaria Nyasaye."
  43,68,"Enywe Abasumba banje, shimulaba noburi inyanga yino tawe, neshimulabeelela tawe."
  43,69,"Balia Abasuubila ebimanyisio biefu mana nibelekhuula khu Nyasaye (nibaba abasalamu)."
  43,70,"""Injile mumukunda kwomwikulu enywe nende abakhaye benyu musangasibwemwo."""
  43,71,"Balihelesibwa luno nende lulia ebisanda nende ebikaye bia idhahabu, ne bilibamwo bia emioyo chikombanga nende ebisangasia tsimoni, ne enywe mulimenyamwo tsinyaanga tsioosi."
  43,72,"Oko niko omukunda kwomwikulu (Janna) okwamulihebwa khulwa kamwakholanga."
  43,73,"Mulibaamwo nende ebiamo ebinji biamulilia khubio."
  43,74,"Toto abetsimbi baliba mushinyasio shia mumulilo kwa Jahannam tsinyanga tsioosi."
  43,75,"Shibalihulusibwa okhurulana nende eshinyasio esho tawe, ne omo baliwesiakhwo omwoyo (okhurulamwo) muno."
  43,76,"Ne shikhwabakholela amabii tawe, halali boo abeene nibo bali abamabii."
  43,77,"Ne balikhupa oluyoka nibalanga: “Ewe Malik! Boolela Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi akhufwisie.” Naye alibaboolela mbu: “Enywe toto omo butswa nimwamulamenya.”"
  43,78,"Toto khwabetsela nende obwatoto, halali abanji mwinywe mwali mwakhaya obwatoto."
  43,79,"Nohomba babusia amalako kabu. Ne toto nefwe babusinjia."
  43,80,"Nohomba baparanga mbu efwe shikhuwulilanga akobwifisi nende kokhumonyana kabu tawe? Eeh tawe. Abarumwa befu bali ninabo bahandikanga kabakholanga."
  43,81,"Boola mbu: “Nyasaye abetsanga nende Omwana, nesie wakhabeele weyimbeli okhumulaama.”"
  43,82,"Ni omutswenufu Nyasaye Omulesi welikulu nende eshialo, Nyasaye Omulesi weshisaala shioluyali ehale nende koosi kabamureetsangakhwo."
  43,83,"Ne baleshe bakoyaane nibabaya, okhula shinga balinyoolana nende inyanga yabalakwa."
  43,84,"Naye niye Nyasaye mwikulu khandi ni Nyasaye mushialo, naye niye Omuchesi, Omumanyi muno."
  43,85,"Ni woluyali ulia owuli nobwami bwomwikulu nende mushialo, nende bioosi bilimwo, ne niye uli nobumanyi bwebise bieyindukho, ne ewuwe ni wamulikalusibwa."
  43,86,"Ne abamulaamanga abalali Ye tawe babula obunyali bwokhusabila Omundu eshileshelo, halali ulia wobuloli bwatoto, nabo bamanya."
  43,87,"Ne nobareeba mbu ni wina wabaloonga bo? Toto bweene balaboola mbu: ""Ni Nyasaye."" Kho ni hena wabakalukhanibungwa?"
  43,88,"Ne okhuboola khukhwe (Omurumwa) mbu: “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, bano ni Abandu balasuubila tawe.”"
  43,89,"Kho baleshele ne baboolele amakhuwa komuleembe. Baliitsa okhumanya!"
